  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day, my father happened to walk in while I was eating with the kippah, and he made a big fuss of it, and he was very mad at my-- at my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] That is one episode that I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was another episode.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that must have been maybe about a year or more even later than that and must have been somewhere in the summer of '39, where I was going to a summer day camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my father used to bring me to that place where they used to take the children from there out of town.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And since I-- and my mother used to prepare some lunch for me to take for the day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was a very bad eater.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I used to take the lunch, and at the corner where we were standing there was a fence-- a wooden fence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that fence had a hole in-- in it, and while I was standing and waiting for the-- for the bus or whatever it was to come and pick us up, I used to threw in that lunch behind that fence.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One day, I wasn't so successful, and my father-- my father caught me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that was another episode that I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was another episode that must have been also probably before the war already, shortly before the war, and that was on [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Passover time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father took me to [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a public-- what's it called-- baths.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was a bath, steamer bath, because the facilities weren't that modern with showers and [INAUDIBLE] in the houses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- my father took me with him, and it was, as I mentioned, Passover.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
